      "raw_text": "Deputy United States Marshal\nCharles P. Pray has seized the out\nfit and tools, worth more than\n$4,000, belonging to H. X. Luce\nand the Standard Building Co. on\nan attachment issued by the gov\neminent.\n\n\nLuce and his company had con-\ntract with the government to con.\nstruct wasteway canal near\nProsser, on Sulphur creek, a part\nof the big government irrigation\nproject, and the agreemnt was that\nin case the work was not finished\nor was abandoned the government\ncould take the tools and finish it.\nLuce failed to complete the work\nand hence the seizure His com.\npany will fight the case in the\nfederal court."
